Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Morel-Lavall√©e lesion' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Ventral' radio button is enabled
And 'Medial' radio button is enabled
And 'Lateral' radio button is enabled
And 'Dorsal' radio button is enabled

And 'Size' input field is enabled

And 'Type I' radio button is enabled
And 'Type II' radio button is enabled
And 'Type III' radio button is enabled
And 'Type IV' radio button is enabled
And 'Type V' radio button is enabled
And 'Type VI' radio button is enabled

And 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled

When I enter any value from 1 to 500 in 'Size' input field
Then '2nd plane' input field is enabled
When I enter any value from 1 to 500 in '2nd plane' input field
Then '3rd plane' input field is enabled

When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled
